{"id":"d=origam-topic-2200//p=d8f61dbb827343bd875ff30d86b7ee05","tags":{"__document_id":["origam-topic-2200"],"__file_type":["text/plain"],"__file_id":["0f2d6bf70b114750bcd3d98aa96c827a"],"__file_part":["4070e084f0114e4e9024437d5ca494bf"],"__part_n":["0"],"__sect_n":["0"],"source":["origam-community"],"category":["docs"],"categoryId":["8"],"topicId":["2200"],"url":["https://community.origam.com/t/imap-loader/2200"],"title":["IMAP Loader"]},"payload":{"url":"","schema":"20231218A","file":"content.txt","text":"# IMAP Loader\n\nCategory: docs\nURL: https://community.origam.com/t/imap-loader/2200\n\n@system (2017-12-31 23:00:00Z):\n IMAP loader allows you to automatically pick up e-mails from an IMAP-enabled mail server. It supports SSL. E-mails are moved to a configurable archive folder after being picked up. \n   WORK QUEUE CLASS \n This loader uses the Mail work queue class. \n   CONFIGURE IMAP LOADER \n To pick up e-mails to your Work Queue from an IMAP account, you have to fill the  External Source  field with  IMAP  on tab Creation and fill in the Connection String as described later. All other fields of the External Source group are not applicable and should remain empty. \n          9404486_516x298  516\u00D7298 5.36 KB         \n   CONFIGURE CONNECTION STRING \n The connection string can consist of the following parts: \n \n \n \n \n  \n  \n \n \n \n \n url \n Url of the IMAP server (e.g.  imap.mycompany.com ) \n \n \n port \n IMAP server\u2019s port number (typically 143 or 993 for SSL encrypted) \n \n \n ssl \n If  True  then the connection will be encrypted (you would probably need to change also the port number). \n \n \n mailbox \n Name of the folder with the incoming e-mails (default is  INBOX ) \n \n \n Dropbox \n Name of the archive folder (where e-mail will be moved after being picked up) \n \n \n attachHtml \n If  True  then the HTML version of the e-mail (if available) will be attached as an attachment to the work queue entry together with other e-mail attachments. \n \n \n badmail \n Name of a folder where e-mails that had problems with loading will be moved to. \n \n \n sanitize \n  2025.2  If  true  invalid XML characters are stripped from the message and the message is further processed, otherwise the message is put to  badmail  folder. \n \n \n \n    Configure User Name and Password \n Enter the account\u2019s username and password to the corresponding fields.","vector_provider":"AI.Ollama.OllamaTextEmbeddingGenerator","vector_generator":"__","last_update":"2026-04-29T00:23:31"},"vector":[-0.029279135,-0.034142416,-0.037007082,0.016047833,-0.010809459,-0.008907168,0.0097028455,-0.0091778925,-0.003545152,0.008075936,0.0030668974,0.00723777,-0.036679175,-0.002568862,0.012578687,0.029559916,0.0034183294,0.018389642,-0.0109963305,-0.020350028,0.02223884,-0.023972923,0.017338052,-0.015169911,-0.0005927195,-0.015143751,-0.012395528,-0.0059922207,-0.0025234022,-0.016031692,-0.031091496,-0.036533114,-0.003877051,0.017018477,0.026432551,0.016766582,-0.003691284,-0.018017204,-0.017343458,0.029942017,-0.0063069137,-0.016334705,-0.015372292,-0.023745146,0.04479342,-0.010441444,0.013104037,-0.014166403,-0.020559946,-0.05800236,0.005546967,-0.013877401,0.008260424,-0.037565168,0.035853617,0.03907143,-0.0070883236,0.0040566525,-0.04183994,-0.00056302187,0.021255204,-0.0013668578,0.0018699968,-0.034795396,-0.028912412,0.011963371,-0.017537864,0.028159996,-0.035138324,-0.019963356,-0.004744417,0.042731866,-0.024049902,-0.006357392,-0.060478244,-0.033391654,0.052305367,-0.0018140704,-0.06198454,0.023158884,-0.0049152793,-0.003284268,0.024026705,0.01281037,-0.02119083,-0.023535352,-0.06471498,0.04353574,0.023354752,0.05151304,-0.009623233,-0.0060164207,0.0042433855,-0.04939181,-0.09166501,-0.018994946,0.035287004,-0.017545821,0.051941104,-0.0001305018,-0.0043951413,0.011667895,-0.012455349,0.011191534,-0.0014941578,-0.027050449,-0.004618547,0.0077271597,-0.03350651,-0.04121816,0.015930677,-0.005989972,0.059532445,-0.01023268